{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572990/extras/Group_10.png?t=1734116107\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We got inspired by games like Getting over it and Peaks of Yore, but they made us think; What if we can actually make people better gamers by changing the concept a bit? So we decided to make it first person, have a narrating coach to guide your progress and have a a nasty enemy voice nagging you for fun's sake. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So what is it about:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>first person</strong> 3D <strong>climbing game</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's really <strong>hard</strong>, but the <strong>coach</strong> will help you get over <strong>your frustrations.</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will <strong>fall</strong> and the &quot;enemy voice&quot; will <strong>laugh at you</strong> for it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No, it's not VR. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Creating legends</strong>: The ultimate goal is to cultivate a <strong>mindset for growth</strong>, rather than <strong>frustration</strong> or <strong>tilting</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Free Climb the Neuroasis Mountain:</strong> Challenge yourself to reach the towering 500-meter summit!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>One-Minute Climbing Challenge:</strong> How far can you ascend when every second counts?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Jaymundr: <i>&quot;Mindform: <strong>THE</strong> <strong>soulslike</strong> of climbing games!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572990/extras/Climb.gif?t=1734116107\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Start of the j